Introduction

Hyebin is a South Korean singer and rapper. She is the leader of the former girl group MOMOLAND. In 2016, she became a contestant on Mnet's reality survival show Finding Momoland. She finished the competition in first place, thus becoming the leader of the girl group MOMOLAND. The group officially debuted on November 10, 2016, with their first mini album "Welcome to Momoland".
